accuracy is critical for detectors like Advanced LIGO, Virgo, KAGRA and next-generation observatories like the Einstein Telescope and Cosmic Explorer 🔭</p> <p>I wanted to make this topic accessible and engaging for everyone—scientists, science enthusiasts, and students alike!</p> <p>Stay tuned for the release of the paper. 🚀</p> <h3 id="gravitational-waves-comic-book">Gravitational-Waves Comic Book</h3> <swiper-container slides-per-view="1" centered-slides="false" slides-per-group-skip="1" grab-cursor="true" keyboard="true" breakpoints="{&quot;769&quot;: {&quot;slidesPerView&quot;: 2, &quot;slidesPerGroup&quot;: 2}}" scrollbar="true" navigation="true"> <swiper-slide> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/GW_comic_1-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/GW_comic_1-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/GW_comic_1-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/GW_comic_1.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </swiper-slide> <swiper-slide> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/GW_comic_2-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/GW_comic_2-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/GW_comic_2-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/GW_comic_2.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </swiper-slide> <swiper-slide> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" srcset="/assets/img/GW_comic_3-480.webp 480w,/assets/img/GW_comic_3-800.webp 800w,/assets/img/GW_comic_3-1400.webp 1400w," type="image/webp" sizes="95vw"/> <img src="/assets/img/GW_comic_3.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="100%" height="auto" loading="eager" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </